This paper is about reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper proposes an algorithm for selecting the state representation in reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of machine learning algorithms. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). 

The paper also deals with decision-making processes and optimization, which are relevant to sub-categories such as cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). 

The paper also mentions regret bounds, which are a common topic in the sub-category of online learning, cs.SY (Systems and Control). 

Finally, the paper proposes an algorithm for minimizing regret, which is a common topic in the sub-category of multi-armed bandits, cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems). 

Therefore, the likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, and cs.MA, ordered from most to least likely.
